steps.html_instructions: Head southeast on Bulatan Jam Besar toward Jalan Ismail
Turn left at Persimpangan Gajah Mati onto Jln Sultanah Zainab/D1
Turn right at Persimpangan Kijang onto the ramp to Jalan Kota Bharu - Pengkalan Kubor/Laluan Persekutuan 3/AH18
Merge onto Jalan Kota Bharu - Pengkalan Kubor/Laluan Persekutuan 3/AH18

At Bulatan Pasir Pekan, take the 2nd exit onto Jalan Kota Bharu - Pengkalan Kubor/Route 134
Pass by Perabot Sayang wakaf Bharu (on the right in 800m)

Slight right onto Jalan Baru/Jalan Kota Bharu - Pengkalan Kubor/Route 134
Continue to follow Jalan Kota Bharu - Pengkalan Kubor/Route 134
Turn left onto Jalan Bunut Susu - Kubang Batang
Continue straight to stay on Jln Bunut Susu/D180

Turn left onto Jalan Lubok Setol/Jalan Panglima Bayu - Rantau Panjang/Route 196
Continue to follow Jalan Panglima Bayu - Rantau Panjang
Turn left toward Jalan Baling - Kuala Kangsar/Jalan Lenggong - Gerik/Route 76
Slight left onto Jalan Baling - Kuala Kangsar/Jalan Lenggong - Gerik/Route 76
Turn left at the 1st cross street onto Jln Toh Mekong
Turn right at the 1st cross street onto Jalan Takong Datok

Turn left at the 1st cross street onto Jln Toh Merah
Destination will be on the right
